{"word":"φρέαρ","slug":"φρέαρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φρέαρ</b></el> <el>(φρέαρ, τό,) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a well</i> (distinguished from <a href='S:κρήνη'><el>κρήνη</el></a>, <i>a spring)</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a tank, cistern, reservoir</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>puteus</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <i>an oil jar</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}